This directory contains Doxygen configuration information
and extra pages for the SCIRun2 documentation.

TO GENERATE THE DOCUMENTATION:

1) Edit the INPUT and EXCLUDE paths in the file SCIRun2.config to 
reflect the location of your SCIRun checkout.

2) Edit the OUTPUT_DIRECTORY, HTML_OUTPUT, LATEX_OUTPUT, etc. paths 
in the file SCIRun2.config to reflect the desired output directories.

3) run "doxygen SCIRun2.config"

TO MODIFY OR ADD CODE DOCUMENTATION
Edit the header file for the desired class using Doxygen formatting.

TO MODIFY THE MAIN AND AUXILIARY PAGES
Edit the appropriate *.dox files found in this directory, or add 
new pages.

FOR MORE INFORMATION
See www.doxygen.org


